<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hang-on">hang on</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-hold-on">1.<strong>抓紧不放；[非正式用语] 不要挂断(hold on)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Hang on to</strong> the rope and don't let go.
抓紧绳子，不要松手。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hang on — I'll just see if he's here.
别挂断，我这就去看看他在不在。</p></div></div>